-- MOVES-Macquarie Capital appoints Peter Davis as managing director
-- 
-- Wed Aug 13, 2014 09:38AM EDT
-- None



Aug 13 (Reuters) - Macquarie Capital, the corporate advisory and capital markets arm of Macquarie Group Ltd <MQG.AX>, appointed Peter Davis as a managing director in its U.S. Financial Institutions Group.

Davis will lead the firm's coverage of the financial technology sector. He joins Macquarie Capital after seven years at Lehman Brothers and Barclays Capital, a unit of British bank Barclays Plc <BARC.L>.